From Dale A Dale Adams Subject Re Adding VRAM to Quadra In article W Stuart Jones writes I want to go from to VRAM on my Quadra How many SIMMS do I need to buy Is the current soldered on the board or do I need to take out the current VRAM before I add more You need to add two VRAM SIMMs VRAM SIMMs will not work in any of the Quadra or Centris There is already of VRAM soldered to the logic You add the two SIMMs to this to give you a total of Dale Adams